{"tid":1092302,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[倒米]曾樂彤新廣告遭抵制 網民齊聲高呼#百nlm","createTime":"2019-04-04T17:06:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T11:11:11.000Z","uid":173693,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7b168947e5f02d2ff1d86590129d8220ef01cb2e","tid":1092302,"uid":173693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T17:06:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1870652926489902/posts/2424850471070142?sfs=xwa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1870652926489902%2Fposts%2F2424850471070142%3Fsfs%3Dxwa&d=Ibp2r5avkWIk14HZtW%2BzJzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=b746ccda\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1870652926489902/posts/2424850471070142?sfs=xwa</a><br />\n<br />\n著名電器產品公司百XX 近日宣傳短片搵來以「咪咀」聞名嘅粗口新人曾樂彤演出，與爺爺陳家樂賣電器，點知近日以一句#micnlm 辣著網民，搞到一眾網民還以顏色，在該公司粉絲專頁發起攻擊，齊聲高呼 #百nlm ，仲抵死咁話以後罷買該公司產品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b0AeH20.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb0AeH20.png&h=c0cb27f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67297bad2faeeff037ef1e29160ccbf341d01320","tid":1092302,"uid":100793,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T17:07:14.000Z","msg":"#micnlm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ac0e239d8e06155157bc48e041c26b756c350f","tid":1092302,"uid":173693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"67297bad2faeeff037ef1e29160ccbf341d01320","tid":1092302,"uid":100793,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T17:07:14.000Z","msg":"#micnlm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T17:08:55.000Z","msg":"#hinlm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3893c618c532d1aef44ef41445ec6c1922c052dc","tid":1092302,"uid":233180,"like":37,"dislike":2,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T17:11:09.000Z","msg":"香港人真係好撚煩<br />\n<br />\n需要團結嘅時候又唔團結 團結埋喺啲濕鳩